{
  "protocol_type": "binary_custom",
  "description": "Modbus RTU 风格协议示例",
  "frame_format": {
    "sync_bytes": "",
    "meta_size": 6,
    "has_crc": true,
    "crc_size": 2,
    "crc_poly": "0xA001",
    "crc_init": "0xFFFF",
    "sample_size": 2,
    "endianness": "big",
    "has_sequence": false,
    "has_channel_id": true,
    "channel_id_offset": 0,
    "sample_count_offset": 4,
    "max_samples": 125
  },
  "notes": [
    "类 Modbus RTU 帧格式:",
    "[ADDR:1B] - 设备地址/通道 ID",
    "[FUNC:1B] - 功能码 (固定为 0x04 读取输入寄存器)",
    "[START:2B] - 起始地址 (big endian)",
    "[CNT:2B] - 寄存器数量 (big endian)",
    "[DATA:CNT×2B] - 数据 (big endian)",
    "[CRC:2B] - CRC-16 Modbus (little endian)",
    "",
    "注意:",
    "- 此示例仅作参考，实际 Modbus 协议需要完整实现",
    "- CRC-16 使用 Modbus 专用多项式 0xA001",
    "- 数据为大端序（big endian）",
    "- CRC 为小端序（little endian）",
    "",
    "使用场景:",
    "- 工业设备数据采集",
    "- 兼容 Modbus 设备",
    "- 需要设备地址的场景"
  ]
}
